column5: I know you are smiles from ear to ear dude.  Jimmy has joined some of the greats  http://www.nascar.com/en_us/news-media/articles/2016/11/20/jimmie-johnson-wins-seventh-sprint-cup-series-championship-homestead-miami.html

Was definitely a dramatic finish.... Im a huge Jimmy fan but cant but feel a wee bit bad for Carl... He's been close to the cup a few times... Kinda like JJ in his early years... Another title for the bow ties!

I thought it was going to be Joey, but man that was a wild finish. Yes Carl made a boner move, but classie of him to step up and say. me bad. Need more to do this. Not blame others for their own screw ups.
